fy_destructible_b1

-----
Ok so finished this map today and it's now time to add it here :)
-----
This is pretty decent fy map imo. Should be optimal for around 10 players. I used time with rounded corners and such for better look and detail. And now to the biggest point of the map.
EVERY WOODEN PART IN THE MAP CAN BE DESTROYED!!
 Yeah that's right. Every part with wooden texture can be shot down. Just look at the screenshots, there's alot things you can destroy! That's why I named it destructible ;)
-----
I didn't have really time for good bug testing, so I'd highly apreciate if you could tell me if you're going to put this on your servers, because I'd like to take a look how it works with much players. Also, please post a comment if you find any bugs or exploits so I can fix them for beta 2 :)
----- Map includes:
-32 player spawns (16 each team) -3D Skybox -Lots of func_breakable entitys -Dark lighting with lots of shadows -Huge amount of decals -Nav -file -And epic sexiness by SwatMat ;)
-----
I hope you have as much fun as I did while making it. Remember to comment, asses and ofcourse test the map ingame so you see all the sexiness by yourself. :) Have fun! I hope you have great time with this map! :)
